{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"87c573c56a","title":"关于部队中急待解决的问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e892cc32ef","index":0,"year":1954,"month":8,"day":3,"articleId":"87c573c56a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"e5fe09703e","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会副主席彭德怀1954年7月28日报告上写给刘少奇的批语。"},{"id":"e697dc8961","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指彭德怀的报告。报告说：最近部队中存在几个急待解决的问题：（一）自三反运动以后，在一部分高级干部中，仍滋长着若千个人享乐、腐化重落的恶劣现象。（二）1954年上半年，发生两件最严重的失密事件。（三）兵员太老，全军现80%的兵，都是参军3年以上的老兵。（四）下层干部的结婚限制，再不宜继续下去。"},{"id":"c29881f3ac","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央政治局1954年8月27日会议决定：（一）关于在一部分干部中滋长着若干个享乐、腐化单落的恶劣现象和严重的失密事件，必须开展适当的斗争和严格执行纪律，由军委在1954年冬或1955年春召开一次解放军全军党代表会议，提出讨论并做出决定。（二）关于兵员问题和下级干部的婚烟问题，待中央讨论兵役法时再行讨论。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0a7b9c3934","type":"title","text":"关于部队中急待解决的问题的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a"},{"id":"e5fe09703e","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a"},{"id":"e697dc8961","type":"paragraph","text":"此件似应在中央会议讨论作出决定问","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a"},{"id":"c29881f3ac","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a"},{"id":"061ee5d6e0","type":"paragraph","text":"八月三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a"}],"page":{"id":"a026340b4b","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"87c573c56a","start":193,"end":193}}}},"__N_SSG":true}